text: Delber Medina Rodríguez (born 12 February 1960) is a Mexican politician from the National Action Party. From 2006 to 2009 he served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Nayarit. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Nayarit Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:National Action Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
